\n      應於收受本命令後7日內向本院陳報，以利合法送達本命\r\n      令。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/NTDV/110%2c%e5%8f%b8%e4%bf%83%2c7755%2c20211119%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"NTDV,110,司促,7755,20211119,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"司促","JNO":"7755","JDATE":"20211119","JTITLE":"支付命令"}